featured_reviews.review_id: This is Ariyalur big mosque. It is very big. This has a good parking space as well. The place is centralized air conditioning. Solar panel works are under progress here. They have a Islamic cemetery here. During Ramadhan you get free sahar here every day for 30 days. You get free nonbu Kanji daily for 30 days. All 5 times prayer offered here. They conduct isthima or religious meetings in between. Overall it is a nice place for worship and religious needs.
